OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBright or
OL,6,Fclear spells continue as showers die
OL,7,Fduring the evening. Cloud will
OL,8,Fincrease towards midnight and
OL,9,Foutbreaks of locally heavy rain spread
OL,10,Fnortheast towards morning.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FCloudy with outbreaks of
OL,13,Flocally heavy rain. This rain will
OL,14,Fclear during the afternoon with the
OL,15,Fchance of a few heavy showers
OL,16,Ffollowing on behind. Warm.
OL,17,
OL,18,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FOutbreaks
OL,19,Fof locally heavy rain Friday clears
OL,20,Fovernight to leave Saturday and Sunday
OL,21,Fmostly dry with sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
